This section will designate the primary stream out method and it's settings. This stream will be displayed in the dashboard. If you choose to use HLS, JPEG, or MJPEG then you can consume the stream through other programs.

Using JPEG stream essentially turns off the primary stream and uses the snapshot bin to get frames.
